thread.title: Another earthquake rocks Chile

author: eTN Global Editor
title: Another earthquake rocks Chile
text:
Sep 21, 2015   
Magnitude 6.5 earthquake rocked Chile today. 
Preliminary Earthquake Report: 
Date-Time • 21 Sep 2015 17:39:58 UTC • 21 Sep 2015 14:39:59 near epicenter 
Location 31.742S 71.635W 
Distances • 46 km (28 mi) WSW of Illapel, Chile • 62 km (38 mi) W of Salamanca, Chile • 87 km (53 mi) NNW of La Ligua, Chile • 121 km (75 mi) NNW of Hacienda La Calera, Chile • 211 km (130 mi) NNW of Santiago, Chile 
Location Uncertainty Horizontal: 4.8 km; Vertical 4.6 km Parameters Nph = 109; Dmin = 118.8 km; Rmss = 1.30 seconds; Gp = 71°
